data.description: Prof photos coming.  Tranquil and picturesque Norris is a sought after town with the feeling of Mayberry.  Once you've ventured here you won't want to leave.  It is convenient to Norris Lake, Clinton TN, Knoxville, TN, Oak Ridge TN and to the mountains that surround this East TN area.  As you walk onto the property you're greeted with a wonderful rocking chair front porch for enjoying long summer nights or just taking in the neighborhood.  The open floorpan as you come through the front door offers a place to enjoy & make memories with family and friends as it flows nicely into a dining area off of the spacious kitchen and leads out to the back deck that overlooks the huge backyard.  The hallway off of the open living area leads to the guest bedrooms, and the main suite with attached bath that is at the back of the home.  There is a nice guest bathroom that serves the two additional bedrooms in this one level ranch home.  The expansive backyard has endless possibilities for use; there is much to be enjoyed in this wonderful home.  You can come into the home and put your personal touch with some updates, including extending the back deck out for greater use.  Norris has a Great City government and City services with Tree lined streets and sidewalks.  There is a Full service community library, Norris-based community theater, there is an Annual July 4th Norris Day celebration with evening fireworks, Summer-time Concerts on the Commons.Quaint compact Town Center can boast of...Large open grassy town commons for recreationLarge town pavilion for public and private eventsOpen air performance stageNorris MuseumNumerous small businesses:  Grocery store, restaurants, post office, dental office, bank, banquet/catering facility, physical therapy center, beauty salon and more.All information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed.  Property is being sold as is.  Buyers must verify all information.  There is no walkway to the front porch, so be cautious when there is snow on the ground.Do not go onto the back deck as it is not sturdy.  Showings are to be made through a Real Estate Agent; do not access the property without a Real Estate Agent.
